VALUES
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00140', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '張貼理髮店大門的對聯，下列選項正確的是：', '["雖云毫末技藝，卻是頂上功夫", "現出廬山真面目，留住秋水舊丰神", "創人間頭等事業，理世上不平東西", "雖無劉阮逢仙術，只效岐黃救世心 技術革新頭頭是道，容光煥發面面皆春"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00141', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '子路問成人，子曰：「若臧武仲之知，公綽之不欲，卞莊子之勇，冉求之藝，文之以禮樂，亦可以為成人矣」 （《論語．憲問》）。下列選項，何者符合「成人」旨意？', '["臧武仲的知足", "孟公綽的廉潔", "卞莊子的勇敢", "冉求的新文藝 禮樂文化薰陶"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00142', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '陳太丘與友期行，期日中。過中不至，太丘舍去。去後乃至。元方時年七歲，門外戲。客問元方：「尊君在不？」 答曰：「待君久不至，已去。」友人便怒曰：「非人哉！與人期行，相委而去。」元方曰：「君與家君期日中， 日中不至，則是無信；對子罵父，則是無禮。」友人慚，下車引之，元方入門不顧（《世說新語．方正》）。 根據上文內容判斷，下列選項正確的是：', '["陳元方表現出天真頑皮的個性", "「尊君」一詞可用「令堂」替換", "陳太丘的朋友是位推諉塞責的人", "本文從反面說明「信」與「禮」的重要性 陳元方年紀雖小，卻能明白「言而有信」的道理"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00143', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '詩人馬佛：「當青春在你的容顏留駐如朝露」、「以歡樂衝決生命一扇扇的鐵門」，所以人生應及時行樂。 下列詩句，何者符合馬佛所說的意思？', '["不如飲美酒，被服紈與素", "人生得意須盡歡，莫使金樽空對月", "枝在牆東花在西，自從落地任風吹", "閒雲潭影日悠悠，物換星移幾度秋 多情自古傷離別，更那堪，冷落清秋節"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00144', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '「四大讀書信念：第一條，要讀喜歡的書；第二條，要讀不喜歡的書；第三條，要在書中讀到自己，反思自 我；第四條，讀書不能替代行動，書裡是二手的人生，去工作、去戀愛、去旅行，真實認真活著，永遠活在 live現場轉播狀態，那才是一手的人生。」下列選項符合上文意旨的是：', '["讀書忌死讀", "讀書貴多不貴精", "盡信書不如無書", "讀萬卷書，行萬里路 讀書破萬卷，下筆如有神"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00145', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列「」內的動物，何者在成語中含有「人品性格」的象徵意義？', '["塞翁失「馬」", "驚弓之「鳥」", "「鶴」立雞群", "「狐」群狗黨 引「狼」入室"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00146', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '「繁華擾攘的羅東鎮，藏著一條名為『浮崙巷』的小徑，巷名充滿文藝感。名稱取自於當地舊名『浮崙仔』， 由於該區地勢高，水患淹不到，遠看像是浮出水面的車輪而得名。隨著街區發展更迭，周邊發展出夜市和商 圈，浮崙巷『鬧中取靜』，只有在地人知道的捷徑，獨樹一格成為文藝風小巷。在地文史工作者說，浮崙巷 正是在地鄉土作家黃春明出生地，早期著作《鑼》便是起源於此。」 這則報導從那幾個面向介紹「浮崙巷」？', '["地名由來", "特產小吃", "街巷特色", "著名地標 在地名人"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00147', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-8bd7a5fb', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為中央銀行貨幣政策的操作目標？', '["貨幣總計數M", "法定存款準備率", "經濟成長率", "貨幣基數 2"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5785234232fd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "691610eabba0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "貨幣銀行學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00148', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-8bd7a5fb', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據費利德曼的現代貨幣需求理論，下列何者與貨幣需求呈正相關？', '["債券報酬率與貨幣報酬率的差距", "預期通貨膨脹率", "恆常所得", "權益證券報酬率與貨幣報酬率的差距"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5785234232fd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "691610eabba0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "貨幣銀行學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-7c4986e7-moex-00149', 'elementary-7c4986e7', 'elementary-7c4986e7-moex-110-8bd7a5fb', 'sub-elementary-7c4986e7-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若目前新臺幣利率3%，美元利率2%，假設購買力平價說與拋補利率平價說、未拋補利率平價說均成立， 則下列敘述何者正確？', '["臺灣通貨膨脹率小於美國通貨膨脹率", "美元呈現溢價", "美元遠期匯率低於現貨匯率", "預期新臺幣升值"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5785234232fd", "answer_pdf_sha1": "691610eabba0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "508", "s": "0502", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "貨幣銀行學大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "金融保險"}'::jsonb, NULL)
